-- Siemens to Cooperate With Abu Dhabi on Smart Grids, Power Grids in Masder
-- B y   B e n e d i k t   K a m m e l
-- 2010-10-19T14:16:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-19/siemens-to-cooperate-with-abu-dhabi-on-smart-grids-power-grids-in-masder.html
Siemens AG, Europe’s largest
engineering company, said it entered an agreement with Abu Dhabi
to cooperate on the Masder City project, including advanced
electricity grids and building technology, according to a
statement released by the Munich-based company today.  Siemens didn’t give a value of the accord.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Benedikt Kammel at 
 bkammel@bloomberg.net  